## Description développeur
Composant généré par le pipeline IA avec fidélité pixel-perfect Figma. À compléter par le développeur.

## Token Mapping (Figma → CSS)
| Propriété CSS | Token | Figma (valeur exacte) | État |
|---|---|---|---|
| background-color | --component-button-primary-bg | #d90a79 | Default (Primary) |
| background-color | --component-button-primary-bg-hover | #1D4ED8 | Hover (Primary) |
| background-color | --component-button-secondary-bg | #FFFFFF | Default (Secondary) |
| background-color | --component-button-ghost-bg | transparent | Default (Ghost) |
| background-color | --component-button-danger-bg | #DC2626 | Default (Danger) |
| background-color | --component-button-disabled-bg | #F3F4F6 | Disabled |
| border-color | --component-button-primary-border | #d90a79 | Default (Primary) |
| border-color | --component-button-secondary-border | --semantic-color-border-default → #D1D5DB | Default (Secondary) |
| color (text) | --component-button-primary-color | #FFFFFF (implied white on primary) | Default (Primary) |
| color (text) | --component-button-secondary-color | #374151 | Default (Secondary) |
| color (text) | --component-button-ghost-color | #374151 | Default (Ghost) |
| color (text) | --component-button-danger-color | #FFFFFF | Default (Danger) |
| border-radius | --component-button-radius | 8px | All |
| border-width | --component-button-border-width | 1px | All |
| font-family | --component-button-font-family | Inter | All |
| font-size (SM) | --component-button-sm-font-size | 14px | SM |
| font-size (MD) | --component-button-md-font-size | 14px | MD |
| font-size (LG) | --component-button-lg-font-size | 16px | LG |
| font-weight | --component-button-font-weight | 600 | All |
| line-height | --component-button-line-height | 20px | All |
| padding (SM) | --component-button-sm-padding | 4px 8px | SM |
| padding (MD) | --component-button-md-padding | 8px 16px | MD |
| padding (LG) | --component-button-lg-padding | 8px 24px | LG |
| gap (SM) | --component-button-sm-gap | 4px | SM |
| gap (MD/LG) | --component-button-md-gap | 8px | MD/LG |
| min-height (SM) | --component-button-sm-min-height | 32px | SM |
| min-height (MD) | --component-button-md-min-height | 40px | MD |
| min-height (LG) | --component-button-lg-min-height | 48px | LG |
| icon-size (SM) | --component-button-sm-icon-size | 16px | SM |
| icon-size (MD) | --component-button-md-icon-size | 20px | MD |
| icon-size (LG) | --component-button-lg-icon-size | 24px | LG |
| transition | --component-button-transition | all 150ms ease-in-out | All |
| outline (focus) | --component-button-focus-ring-color | #d90a79 (primary.500) | Focus |
| outline-width | --component-button-focus-ring-width | 2px | Focus |
| outline-offset | --component-button-focus-ring-offset | 2px | Focus |
| opacity | — | 0.5 | Disabled |

## Do & Don't
✅ **Do**
- Utiliser les CSS custom properties (var(--component-*))
- Respecter les états interactifs (hover, active, focus, disabled)
- Vérifier la fidélité visuelle avec la maquette Figma

❌ **Don't**
- Ne pas utiliser de valeurs brutes (px, #hex) — utiliser les tokens
- Ne pas supprimer les états d'accessibilité (:focus-visible)
- Ne pas modifier les dimensions sans vérifier la spec Figma

## 💻 Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const { useState } = React;

const __css = `/* ============================================================
   COMPONENT TOKENS — Button
   (Mapped from Design System tokens + Figma spec)
   ============================================================ */
:root {
  /* --- Primary variant --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.bg — Figma: #d90a79 */
  --component-button-primary-bg: var(--component-button-primary-bg, /* FALLBACK */ #d90a79);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.bg-hover — Figma: #1D4ED8 */
  --component-button-primary-bg-hover: var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #1D4ED8);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.color — Figma: #FFFFFF */
  --component-button-primary-color: var(--component-button-primary-color, /* FALLBACK */ #FFFFFF);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.primary.border — Figma: #d90a79 */
  --component-button-primary-border: var(--component-button-primary-border, /* FALLBACK */ #d90a79);

  /* --- Secondary variant --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.bg — Figma: #FFFFFF */
  --component-button-secondary-bg: var(--component-button-secondary-bg, /* FALLBACK */ #FFFFFF);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.color — Figma: #374151 */
  --component-button-secondary-color: var(--component-button-secondary-color, /* FALLBACK */ #374151);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.border — Figma: #D1D5DB */
  --component-button-secondary-border: var(--semantic-color-border-default, /* FALLBACK */ #D1D5DB);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.secondary.bg-hover — Figma: implied ~#F9FAFB */
  --component-button-secondary-bg-hover: var(--component-button-secondary-bg-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #F9FAFB);

  /* --- Ghost variant --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.bg — Figma: transparent */
  --component-button-ghost-bg: transparent;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.color — Figma: #374151 */
  --component-button-ghost-color: var(--component-button-ghost-color, /* FALLBACK */ #374151);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.ghost.bg-hover — Figma: implied ~#F3F4F6 */
  --component-button-ghost-bg-hover: var(--component-button-ghost-bg-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #F3F4F6);

  /* --- Danger variant --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.danger.bg — Figma: #DC2626 */
  --component-button-danger-bg: var(--component-button-danger-bg, /* FALLBACK */ #DC2626);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.danger.color — Figma: #FFFFFF */
  --component-button-danger-color: var(--component-button-danger-color, /* FALLBACK */ #FFFFFF);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.danger.bg-hover — Figma: implied ~#B91C1C */
  --component-button-danger-bg-hover: var(--component-button-danger-bg-hover, /* FALLBACK */ #B91C1C);

  /* --- Disabled state --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.disabled.bg — Figma: #F3F4F6 */
  --component-button-disabled-bg: var(--component-button-disabled-bg, /* FALLBACK */ #F3F4F6);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.disabled.color — Figma: #9CA3AF implied */
  --component-button-disabled-color: var(--component-button-disabled-color, /* FALLBACK */ #9CA3AF);

  /* --- Shape & border --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.radius — Figma: 8px */
  --component-button-radius: var(--radius-md, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.border-width — Figma: 1px */
  --component-button-border-width: var(--borderWidth-default, /* FALLBACK */ 1px);

  /* --- Typography --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.font-family — Figma: Inter */
  --component-button-font-family: var(--font-family-default, /* FALLBACK */ 'Inter', sans-serif);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.font-weight — Figma: 600 */
  --component-button-font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold, /* FALLBACK */ 600);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.line-height — Figma: 20px */
  --component-button-line-height: var(--font-lineHeight-normal, /* FALLBACK */ 20px);

  /* --- Size tokens — SM --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.sm.padding-x — Figma: 8px */
  --component-button-sm-padding-x: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.sm.padding-y — Figma: 4px */
  --component-button-sm-padding-y: var(--spacing-xs, /* FALLBACK */ 4px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.sm.font-size — Figma: 14px */
  --component-button-sm-font-size: var(--font-size-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 14px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.sm.gap — Figma: 4px */
  --component-button-sm-gap: var(--spacing-xs, /* FALLBACK */ 4px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.sm.min-height — Figma: 32px */
  --component-button-sm-min-height: 32px;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.sm.icon-size — Figma: 16px */
  --component-button-sm-icon-size: 16px;

  /* --- Size tokens — MD --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.md.padding-x — Figma: 16px */
  --component-button-md-padding-x: var(--spacing-md, /* FALLBACK */ 16px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.md.padding-y — Figma: 8px */
  --component-button-md-padding-y: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.md.font-size — Figma: 14px */
  --component-button-md-font-size: var(--font-size-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 14px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.md.gap — Figma: 8px */
  --component-button-md-gap: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.md.min-height — Figma: 40px */
  --component-button-md-min-height: 40px;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.md.icon-size — Figma: 20px */
  --component-button-md-icon-size: 20px;

  /* --- Size tokens — LG --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.lg.padding-x — Figma: 24px */
  --component-button-lg-padding-x: var(--spacing-lg, /* FALLBACK */ 24px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.lg.padding-y — Figma: 8px */
  --component-button-lg-padding-y: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.lg.font-size — Figma: 16px */
  --component-button-lg-font-size: var(--font-size-md, /* FALLBACK */ 16px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.lg.gap — Figma: 8px */
  --component-button-lg-gap: var(--spacing-sm, /* FALLBACK */ 8px);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.lg.min-height — Figma: 48px */
  --component-button-lg-min-height: 48px;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.lg.icon-size — Figma: 24px */
  --component-button-lg-icon-size: 24px;

  /* --- Interaction --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.transition — Figma: all 150ms ease-in-out */
  --component-button-transition: all 150ms ease-in-out;

  /* --- Focus ring --- */
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.focus.ring-color — Figma: #d90a79 */
  --component-button-focus-ring-color: var(--semantic-color-border-emphasis, /* FALLBACK */ #d90a79);
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.focus.ring-width — Figma: 2px */
  --component-button-focus-ring-width: 2px;
  /* ⚠️ TOKEN_MANQUANT: component.button.focus.ring-offset — Figma: 2px */
  --component-button-focus-ring-offset: 2px;
}

/* ============================================================
   BASE STYLES
   ============================================================ */
.button {
  /* Layout (Figma auto-layout HORIZONTAL) */
  display: inline-flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;

  /* Shape */
  border-radius: var(--component-button-radius);
  border-style: solid;
  border-width: var(--component-button-border-width);

  /* Typography */
  font-family: var(--component-button-font-family);
  font-weight: var(--component-button-font-weight);
  line-height: var(--component-button-line-height);
  text-align: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;

  /* Interaction */
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: var(--component-button-transition);
  user-select: none;
  -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;

  /* Reset */
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  outline: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* Focus visible — WCAG AA */
.button:focus-visible {
  outline: var(--component-button-focus-ring-width) solid var(--component-button-focus-ring-color);
  outline-offset: var(--component-button-focus-ring-offset);
}

/* Icon inside button */
.button__icon {
  display: inline-flex;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ============================================================
   SIZE MODIFIERS
   ============================================================ */

/* SM */
.button--sm {
  padding: var(--component-button-sm-padding-y) var(--component-button-sm-padding-x);
  gap: var(--component-button-sm-gap);
  min-height: var(--component-button-sm-min-height);
  font-size: var(--component-button-sm-font-size);
}

.button--sm .button__icon {
  width: var(--component-button-sm-icon-size);
  height: var(--component-button-sm-icon-size);
}

/* MD (default) */
.button--md {
  padding: var(--component-button-md-padding-y) var(--component-button-md-padding-x);
  gap: var(--component-button-md-gap);
  min-height: var(--component-button-md-min-height);
  font-size: var(--component-button-md-font-size);
}

.button--md .button__icon {
  width: var(--component-button-md-icon-size);
  height: var(--component-button-md-icon-size);
}

/* LG */
.button--lg {
  padding: var(--component-button-lg-padding-y) var(--component-button-lg-padding-x);
  gap: var(--component-button-lg-gap);
  min-height: var(--component-button-lg-min-height);
  font-size: var(--component-button-lg-font-size);
}

.button--lg .button__icon {
  width: var(--component-button-lg-icon-size);
  height: var(--component-button-lg-icon-size);
}

/* ============================================================
   VARIANT: PRIMARY (default)
   Figma: bg #d90a79, border #d90a79, text #FFFFFF
   ============================================================ */
.button--primary {
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg);
  border-color: var(--component-button-primary-border);
  color: var(--component-button-primary-color);
}

.button--primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
  /* Figma: hover bg #1D4ED8 */
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover);
  border-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover);
}

.button--primary:active:not(:disabled) {
  /* Figma: active — darkened primary, implied */
  background-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover);
  border-color: var(--component-button-primary-bg-hover);
  filter: brightness(0.9);
}

/* ============================================================
   VARIANT: SECONDARY
   Figma: bg #FFFFFF, border #D1D5DB, text #374151
   ============================================================ */
.button--secondary {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg);
  border-color: var(--component-button-secondary-border);
  color: var(--component-button-secondary-color);
}

.button--secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg-hover);
  border-color: var(--component-button-secondary-border);
}

.button--secondary:active:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-secondary-bg-hover);
  filter: brightness(0.97);
}

/* ============================================================
   VARIANT: GHOST
   Figma: bg transparent, no border, text #374151
   ============================================================ */
.button--ghost {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg);
  border-color: transparent;
  color: var(--component-button-ghost-color);
}

.button--ghost:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg-hover);
  border-color: transparent;
}

.button--ghost:active:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-ghost-bg-hover);
  filter: brightness(0.95);
}

/* ============================================================
   VARIANT: DANGER
   Figma: bg #DC2626, text #FFFFFF
   ============================================================ */
.button--danger {
  background-color: var(--component-button-danger-bg);
  border-color: var(--component-button-danger-bg);
  color: var(--component-button-danger-color);
}

.button--danger:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-danger-bg-hover);
  border-color: var(--component-button-danger-bg-hover);
}

.button--danger:active:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--component-button-danger-bg-hover);
  filter: brightness(0.9);
}

/* ============================================================
   DISABLED STATE
   Figma: bg #F3F4F6, opacity 0.5
   ============================================================ */
.button:disabled,
.button[aria-disabled="true"] {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Specific disabled bg override from Figma spec */
.button--primary:disabled,
.button--primary[aria-disabled="true"] {
  background-color: var(--component-button-disabled-bg);
  border-color: var(--component-button-disabled-bg);
  color: var(--component-button-disabled-color);
}

/* ============================================================
   ICON-ONLY BUTTON (square)
   ============================================================ */
.button--icon-only {
  padding: var(--component-button-md-padding-y);
  aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
  min-width: var(--component-button-md-min-height);
}

.button--icon-only.button--sm {
  padding: var(--component-button-sm-padding-y);
  min-width: var(--component-button-sm-min-height);
}

.button--icon-only.button--lg {
  padding: var(--component-button-lg-padding-y);
  min-width: var(--component-button-lg-min-height);
}

/* ============================================================
   FULL WIDTH
   ============================================================ */
.button--full-width {
  width: 100%;
}

/* ============================================================
   LOADING STATE
   ============================================================ */
.button--loading {
  cursor: wait;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.button__spinner {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 1em;
  height: 1em;
  border: 2px solid currentColor;
  border-top-color: transparent;
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: button-spin 0.6s linear infinite;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

@keyframes button-spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}`;

const Button = ({ variant = '', size = 'md', disabled = false, children }) => {
  const sizeClass = size !== 'md' ? ' button--' + size : '';
  const variantClass = variant ? ' button--' + variant : '';
  const disabledClass = disabled ? ' button--disabled' : '';
  return (
    <button className={`button${sizeClass}${variantClass}${disabledClass}`} disabled={disabled}>{children}</button>
  );
};

const Demo = () => {
  const [size, setSize] = useState("md");
  const [disabled, setDisabled] = useState(false);

  return (
    <div style={{ padding: "24px", fontFamily: "system-ui, sans-serif" }}>
      <style>{__css}</style>

      <div style={{ marginBottom: "24px", display: "flex", gap: "8px", alignItems: "center" }}>
        <select value={size} onChange={e => setSize(e.target.value)} style={{ padding: "4px 8px", borderRadius: "4px", border: "1px solid #ccc" }}>
          <option value="sm">Small</option>
          <option value="md">Medium</option>
          <option value="lg">Large</option>
        </select>
        <label style={{ fontSize: "14px" }}><input type="checkbox" checked={disabled} onChange={e => setDisabled(e.target.checked)} /> Disabled</label>
      </div>

      <p style={{ fontSize: "11px", fontWeight: 600, textTransform: "uppercase", letterSpacing: "0.08em", color: "#6b7280", marginBottom: "12px" }}>Variants</p>
      <div style={{ display: "flex", flexWrap: "wrap", gap: "12px", marginBottom: "24px" }}>
        <Button variant="primary" size={size} disabled={disabled}>primary</Button>
        <Button variant="secondary" size={size} disabled={disabled}>secondary</Button>
        <Button variant="danger" size={size} disabled={disabled}>danger</Button>
        <Button variant="icon-only" size={size} disabled={disabled}>icon-only</Button>
        <Button variant="full-width" size={size} disabled={disabled}>full-width</Button>
        <Button variant="loading" size={size} disabled={disabled}>loading</Button>
      </div>

      <p style={{ fontSize: "11px", fontWeight: 600, textTransform: "uppercase", letterSpacing: "0.08em", color: "#6b7280", marginBottom: "12px" }}>Sizes</p>
      <div style={{ display: "flex", flexWrap: "wrap", gap: "12px", alignItems: "center" }}>
        <Button variant="primary" size="sm">SM</Button>
        <Button variant="primary" size="md">MD</Button>
        <Button variant="primary" size="lg">LG</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

render(<Demo />);
```

