## Token Mapping (Figma → CSS)
| Propriété CSS | Token | Figma (valeur exacte) | État |
|---|---|---|---|
| background-color | `--component-input-bg-default` → `--semantic-color-bg-primary` | #FFFFFF | default |
| background-color | `--component-input-bg-disabled` → `--semantic-color-bg-disabled` | #F9FAFB | disabled |
| color | `--component-input-text-default` → `--semantic-color-text-primary` | (inherited) | default |
| color | `--component-input-text-placeholder` → `--semantic-color-text-tertiary` | (inherited) | placeholder |
| color | `--component-input-text-disabled` → `--semantic-color-text-disabled` | #D1D5DB | disabled |
| border-color | `--component-input-border-default` → `--semantic-color-border-default` | #D1D5DB | default |
| border-color | `--component-input-border-hover` → `--semantic-color-border-strong` | (hover) | hover |
| border-color | `--component-input-border-focus` → `--semantic-color-border-focus` | #3B82F6 | focus |
| border-color | `--component-input-border-error` → `--semantic-color-danger-500` | #DC2626 | error |
| border-color | `--component-input-border-disabled` → `--semantic-color-border-disabled` | #D1D5DB | disabled |
| border-width | `--component-input-border-width` → `--semantic-border-width-default` | 1px | default |
| border-width | — | 2px | focus |
| border-radius | `--component-input-radius` → `--semantic-radius-md` | 8px | all |
| padding (SM) | `--component-input-size-sm-padding-x` / `--component-input-size-sm-padding-y` | 8px / 4px | sm |
| min-height (SM) | `--component-input-size-sm-min-height` | 32px | sm |
| font-size (SM) | `--component-input-size-sm-font-size` → `--semantic-font-size-sm` | 14px | sm |
| padding (MD) | `--component-input-size-md-padding-x` / `--component-input-size-md-padding-y` | 8px / 8px | md |
| min-height (MD) | `--component-input-size-md-min-height` | 40px | md |
| font-size (MD) | `--component-input-size-md-font-size` → `--semantic-font-size-md` | 16px | md |
| padding (LG) | `--component-input-size-lg-padding-x` / `--component-input-size-lg-padding-y` | 16px / 8px | lg |
| min-height (LG) | `--component-input-size-lg-min-height` | 48px | lg |
| font-size (LG) | `--component-input-size-lg-font-size` → `--semantic-font-size-lg` | 18px | lg |
| gap | — | 8px | all |
| align-items | — | center | all |
| font-family | `--semantic-font-family-sans` | Inter | all |
| font-weight | `--semantic-font-weight-regular` | 400 | all |
| line-height | `--semantic-line-height-normal` | 24px | all |

## Do & Don't
✅ **Do**
- Utiliser les CSS custom properties (var(--component-*))
- Respecter les états interactifs (hover, active, focus, disabled)
- Vérifier la fidélité visuelle avec la maquette Figma

❌ **Don't**
- Ne pas utiliser de valeurs brutes (px, #hex) — utiliser les tokens
- Ne pas supprimer les états d'accessibilité (:focus-visible)
- Ne pas modifier les dimensions sans vérifier la spec Figma

